    accent: "#4878b8", servings: 4,
    description: "The great sauce of Lyon — caramelised onions deglazed with white wine and vinegar, enriched with demi-glace. Robust, sweet-sour, and deeply satisfying. A cornerstone of Lyonnaise cuisine.",
    pairings: ["Lyonnaise Sausages", "Pan-Fried Pork", "Leftover Roast Beef", "Fried Eggs"],
    children: [],
