    accent: "#2870b0", servings: 4,
    description: "A compound butter sauce of the simplest kind — maître d'hôtel butter enriched with meat glaze and perfumed with tarragon. Served melting over grilled fish or steaks, it is one of the most effortlessly elegant sauces in the French canon.",
