    accent: "#1888b0", servings: 4,
    description: "A short, sharp acidulated broth for poaching fish, shellfish, and vegetables. Not a stock to be reduced or built upon, but a poaching medium that perfumes the food cooked within it. Quick to make and indispensable.",
