    tagline: "The Game Stock", difficulty: "Medium", time: "4–5 hrs",
    accent: "#1860a0", servings: 4,
    description: "A dark, intensely flavoured stock of roasted game bones — venison, hare, pheasant carcasses, or wild boar — with juniper berries, red wine, and root vegetables. The essential base of all great game sauces: Poivrade, Grand Veneur, and beyond.",
    pairings: ["Sauce Poivrade", "Sauce Grand Veneur", "Sauce Genevoise", "Braised Venison"],
