    accent: "#c8a060", servings: 6,
    description: "The classic Breton bean preparation: dried white haricot beans slowly braised with tomatoes, onions, garlic, thyme, and parsley until they are completely tender and have absorbed the flavours of the braise. Inseparable from the gigot d'agneau on a French Sunday table.",
    pairings: ["Gigot d'Agneau", "Roast Lamb", "Red Bordeaux", "Côtes du Rhône"],
    children: [],
