    accent: "#c8a840", servings: 2,
    description: "A whole gilt-head bream stuffed with lemon, garlic, thyme, and fennel fronds, roasted on a bed of sliced fennel and tomatoes with olive oil. The simplest and most satisfying way to cook the best fish in the Mediterranean.",
