    accent: "#8a5818", servings: 4,
    description: "A refined version of the gratinéed onion soup using aged Comté rather than Gruyère, with a splash of Vin Jaune from the Jura for complexity. The deep, nutty sweetness of Comté and the oxidative character of Vin Jaune elevate the soup into something distinctly Franc-Comtois.",
