    description: "The great yeasted cake of Alsace, baked in its distinctive fluted mould: a rich brioche-like dough studded with rum-soaked sultanas and lined with whole almonds, which caramelise against the mould during baking. Eaten at Sunday breakfast with café au lait, and at Christmas.",
