    accent: "#c8a030", servings: 4,
    description: "Fresh sardines — the quintessential summer fish of the Mediterranean — grilled whole over charcoal with nothing but sea salt, served with crusty bread and a glass of Bandol rosé. The simplest preparation is the best when the fish is perfectly fresh. Found from the Côte d'Azur to Brittany, wherever there is a harbour and a grill.",
    pairings: ["Bandol Rosé", "Picpoul de Pinet", "Rosé de Provence", "Crusty Baguette"],
