    accent: "#c82040", servings: 8,
    description: "The most beautiful tart in a Parisian pâtisserie window: a pâte sucrée base spread with vanilla crème pâtissière, covered in glistening rows of halved strawberries. Everything depends on the quality of the fruit — use only perfectly ripe strawberries in season. Glazed with warm apricot for the characteristic sheen.",
